Modifying MySQL DB in Live production environment with downtime
Take DB backup
Block access to DB
Connect to Database using mySQL client 
Perform updates and modifications
Enable connection to DB
Resume operations

Modifying MySQL DB in Live production environment without downtime
Take DB backup
Using Percona Toolkit to perform DB updates to temp DB and perform dry runs before applying to actual database.

